casebody.data:
CITY OF TAUNTON, MASSACHUSETTS, petitioner,
v.
ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION AGENCY. No. 18-446. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 19, 2019.

Motion of City of Dover, New Hampshire for leave to file out of time a brief as amicus curiae denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the First Circuit denied.
